  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00773', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-111-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關經濟變數在景氣循環的行為上，下列何者正確？', '["美國供應管理協會的新訂單指數（ISMnewordersindex）是一種順循環（procyclical）且領先（leading） 的變數", "消費是一種逆循環（countercyclical）且同時性（coincident）的變數", "企業固定投資（businessfixedinvestment）是一種順循環且同時性的變數，並且其波動幅度小於消費", "股價是一種順循環且落後（lagging）的變數"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9ca9da4c9d41", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8f8f31d133df", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "511", "s": "0506", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00774', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-111-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '人口成長率提高會對長期經濟成長率造成有利的影響，是因為它導致：', '["人力資本增加", "資本—勞動比率提高", "資本—勞動比率降低", "儲蓄率提高"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9ca9da4c9d41", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8f8f31d133df", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "511", "s": "0506", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
